    {
      "type": "text", "id": "before_body", "x": 78, "y": 268, "width": 304, "height": 100,
      "text": "A weak standard let a little\nlow-value work slip through.\n\nThe cost was small —\na few bad PRs a week,\ncaught by a careful reviewer.", "originalText": "A weak standard let a little\nlow-value work slip through.\n\nThe cost was small —\na few bad PRs a week,\ncaught by a careful reviewer.",
