    {
      "type": "text", "id": "after_body", "x": 508, "y": 272, "width": 244, "height": 100,
      "text": "The standard never changed.\nBut output went 50x.\n\nNow it's a flood of plausible,\nlow-value work — and the\nreviewer cannot keep up.", "originalText": "The standard never changed.\nBut output went 50x.\n\nNow it's a flood of plausible,\nlow-value work — and the\nreviewer cannot keep up.",
