      "type": "text", "id": "caption", "x": 40, "y": 406, "width": 760, "height": 18,
      "text": "Strong standards are not optional overhead — at scale they are the only thing holding the line.", "originalText": "Strong standards are not optional overhead — at scale they are the only thing holding the line.",
